OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start with some sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Cloud will tend to increase
OL,7,Fthroughout the day though with some
OL,8,Fshowers developing throughout the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Feeling a little warmer but
OL,10,Ftemperatures still below average.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FScattered showers continuing
OL,13,Fovernight with some clearer spells in-
OL,14,Fbetween. Showers perhaps becoming more
OL,15,Forganised and heavier later in the
OL,16,Fnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
