OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fscattered showers, with some heavier
OL,7,Fshowers possible. Cloud building later
OL,8,Fwith some wet and windy weather
OL,9,Farriving by evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRain
OL,12,Fclearing on Tuesday to a mix of
OL,13,Fsunshine and blustery showers. Further
OL,14,Fshowers possible on Wednesday, then
OL,15,Fturning drier, brighter and warmer on
OL,16,FThursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
